snippet.title: Rotaeno Game Trailer
snippet.description:
"I wish it would rain tomorrow so gym class gets canceled."
Ilot never thought that the rain would fall for ten years.
 
Rising above the rain of her childhood, our heroine will travel to the stars in search of hope.
 
Rotaeno, the revolutionary rhythm game
launches on May 30!
Pre-register now:
iOS: https://apps.apple.com/app/1614771445
Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.xd.rotaeno.googleplay

BGM: The Promised Land by Iris feat. LynH
